dict.acceptation: 搬家；行动；进展；（机器等）开动；

sent.orig: Before the formal MOVE plan beginning, we will still move the machines to the new building.
sent.trans: 在正式的MOVE计划实施时，还是会移机新大楼的。

sent.orig: To move a category, click Move Up or Move Down in the category's row.
sent.trans: 想移动分区时，在分区行中按下往上移动或往下移动。

sent.orig: Matt: Let's go. Move, move, move! Where is he?
sent.trans: 我们走，快点，快点，快点！他在哪？

sent.orig: Move your arms. Move your legs. Move your body, Mowgli.
sent.trans: 动动你的胳膊。动动你的脚。动动你的身体，无忌。

sent.orig: Moving services-long short-distance move, to move plants, moving offices, discharge counter, move the piano.
sent.trans: 搬家服务--长短途搬家、搬厂、搬写字楼、卸货柜、搬钢琴。
